title: I'm not a nice guy, veganism is not just instagram models and hippies.
description:
And this isn't an academic lecture.  I guess this could have been titled, "I am not a hippy".


This video is comprised of excerpts from a longer video titled, "Life isn't fair, save the planet anyway."  You can still see that video here: https://youtu.be/qDQa-DcDUco
